commentary: Haseeb Amjad to Noor Ali Zadran, OUT Homer Simpson cricket by Noor Ali here! Pushes a drive back down the track, Usman had been backing up, gets back in time to beat the throw, Noor Ali had kept on ambling down the crease, the throw comes back towards him and knocks down his stumps and he's wondering on the long walk back, as we are, how on earth he could get out like that
shortText: Haseeb Amjad to Noor Ali Zadran, OUT
text: Homer Simpson cricket by Noor Ali here! Pushes a drive back down the track, Usman had been backing up, gets back in time to beat the throw, Noor Ali had kept on ambling down the crease, the throw comes back towards him and knocks down his stumps and he's wondering on the long walk back, as we are, how on earth he could get out like that

commentary: Nizakat Khan to Mohammad Nabi, 5 wides An anticlimactic end to a game that was in Afghanistan's control from the three-quarter point of the Hong Kong innings, 216 was unlikely to be enough on a slow but true batting surface. Afghanistan's bowlers all did well, Mirwais the pick with 0-25 off his 10 overs, Hamza and Nabi taking 5-55 off their combined 20. Afghanistan's debutant and Man of the Match Usman Ghani played some audacious strokes on his way to 70 off 68 and with Hong Kong dropping five catches, Afghanistan raced away with the game.
shortText: Nizakat Khan to Mohammad Nabi, 5 wides
text: An anticlimactic end to a game that was in Afghanistan's control from the three-quarter point of the Hong Kong innings, 216 was unlikely to be enough on a slow but true batting surface. Afghanistan's bowlers all did well, Mirwais the pick with 0-25 off his 10 overs, Hamza and Nabi taking 5-55 off their combined 20. Afghanistan's debutant and Man of the Match Usman Ghani played some audacious strokes on his way to 70 off 68 and with Hong Kong dropping five catches, Afghanistan raced away with the game.
